@api = http://localhost:5000

### Test to get all events
GET {{api}}/events

### Test to get an existing event -> GET {{api}}/events/<valid id>
GET {{api}}/events/6079b03f6202145d5d38fce5

### Test to get an non-existing event -> GET {{api}}/events/<not valid id>
GET {{api}}/events/nonexistingevent

### Test to create a valid event
POST {{api}}/events/
Content-Type: application/json

